docs.title: Scripts
docs.text:
• The Strongest Battlegrounds - Scripts for The Strongest Battlegrounds. Features:
    • 'Moveset Templates' - Templates to create custom moveset scripts.
    • 'Custom Moveset Scripts' - Features:
      • Manipulator of Blood - Script
  • Universal - Universal scripts to be used in any game. Coming in the future.
  • Modules - Modules to code easier. Coming in the future.
